Subject: [PATCH 19/22] Add back navigation ABI
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

A Ladybird remembers one road in its stack,
It checks native truth before flying Back.
Crashes dim the arrow; futures stay away,
And Started—not wishful thinking—rules the day.
